name: Chainsaw's Evil Death Match Version 2.0
description: What this is, is an upgrade of CSEVILDM.WAD. I have done is make the level more playable, added a few rooms, a few more details, among other things, and made this the BEST WAD OF ALL TIME. NOTE: This level is NOT to be confused with CS EVIL DEATH MATCH 2, which is the sequel to CSEVILDM, this file is version 2.0 of CSEVILDM.
